  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2050561">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2050561/" class="title-link">历史补习课 -- 许倬云帮我理脉络</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2050561"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3630246/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3630246-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3630246/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">一块肉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-01"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-01 15:37:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2050561_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  关键词: 台湾，“吊诡”。  本来想去买黄仁宇的历史大脉络，可是却意外碰到这本让我看了两眼变决心要买的书。 用一句许老的话就是很“吊诡”。   一本书把中外古代现代史一网打尽是很难得一件事。本书却不在细节多费笔墨，主要表达了作者对若干历史事件相互联系的一种看法，以...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2050561/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2050561_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2050561_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





